324e395b67a8dd21" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.005ex; width:31.385ex; height:5.343ex;" alt="\\operatorname {csch} \\,x={\\frac {1}{\\sinh x}}={\\frac {2}{e^{x}-e^{-x}}}=" /></span></dd>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>e</mi>\n                <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>e</mi>\n                <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </msup>\n              <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>e</mi>\n                <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                  <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>e</mi>\n                <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                  <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>,</mo>\n        <mspace width="2em" />\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2260;<!-- \xe2\x89\xa0 --></mo>\n        <mn>0.</mn>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle ={\\frac {2e^{x}}{e^{2x}-1}}={\\frac {2e^{-x}}{1-e^{-2x}}},\\qquad x\\neq 0.}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/1a553f17e9dd0af7759e18ff4c78a294598a09f5" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.171ex; width:34.754ex; height:5.509ex;" alt="{\\displaystyle ={\\frac {2e^{x}}{e^{2x}-1}}={\\frac {2e^{-x}}{1-e^{-2x}}},\\qquad x\\neq 0.}" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p>The hyperbolic functions may be defined as solutions of <a href="/wiki/Differential_equation" title="Differential equation">differential equations</a>: The hyperbolic sine and cosine are the unique solution <span class="texhtml">(<i>s</i>, <i>c</i>)</span> of the system</p>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mtable columnalign="right left right left right left right left right left right left" rowspacing="3pt" columnspacing="0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em" displaystyle="true">\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>c</mi>\n                  <mo>&#x2032;</mo>\n                </msup>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mi>s</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>s</mi>\n                  <mo>&#x2032;</mo>\n                </msup>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mi>c</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n          </mtable>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}c\'(x)&amp;=s(x)\\\\s\'(x)&amp;=c(x)\\end{aligned}}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/d4f3c8961843fcf9ec06ed0e20010d9561aff47f" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.505ex; width:13.095ex; height:6.176ex;" alt="{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}c&#039;(x)&amp;=s(x)\\\\s&#039;(x)&amp;=c(x)\\end{aligned}}}" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n<p>such that <span class="texhtml"><i>s</i>(0) = 0</span> and <span class="texhtml"><i>c</i>(0) = 1</span>.</p>\n<p>They are also the unique solution of the equation <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <msup>\n          <mi>f</mi>\n          <mo>&#x2033;</mo>\n        </msup>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mi>f</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n        <mo>,</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle f\'\'(x)=f(x),}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/c73de5c3459e2b41cc7ade31c4f2f7ecf61257f7" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:13.879ex; height:3.009ex;" alt="{\\displaystyle f&#039;&#039;(x)=f(x),}" /></span> such that <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mi>f</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mn>1</mn>\n        <mo>,</mo>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>f</mi>\n          <mo>&#x2032;</mo>\n        </msup>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n        <mo>,</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle f(0)=1,f\'(0)=0,}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/f11dc0a59a88727cc2a72760053d62a9f682e315" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:19.584ex; height:3.009ex;" alt="{\\displaystyle f(0)=1,f&#039;(0)=0,}" /></span> for the hyperbolic cosine, and <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mi>f</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n        <mo>,</mo>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>f</mi>\n          <mo>&#x2032;</mo>\n        </msup>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mn>1</mn>\n        <mo>,</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle f(0)=0,f\'(0)=1,}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/7d794a52bad9e621360d1f5abbe7a33137996b4b" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:19.584ex; height:3.009ex;" alt="{\\displaystyle f(0)=0,f&#039;(0)=1,}" /></span> for the hyperbolic sine.</p>\n<p>Hyperbolic functions may also be deduced from <a href="/wiki/Trigonometric_function" class="mw-redirect" title="Trigonometric function">trigonometric functions</a> with <a href="/wiki/Complex_number" title="Complex number">complex</a> arguments:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hyperbolic sine:</li>\n</ul>\n<dl>\n<dd>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mi>sinh</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n        <mi>i</mi>\n        <mi>sin</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mi>i</mi>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle \\sinh x=-i\\sin(ix)}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/39c2728fffaf0edc28190c489b3b77126e1d9e05" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:18.915ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="\\sinh x=-i\\sin(ix)" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<ul>\n<li>Hyperbolic cosine:</li>\n</ul>\n<dl>\n<dd>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mi>cosh</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mi>cos</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mi>i</mi>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle \\cosh x=\\cos(ix)}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/91a741d1a05cdc0f12c4f4d6cad81bd7bdfd4385" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:16.407ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="\\cosh x=\\cos(ix)" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<ul>\n<li>Hyperbolic tangent:</li>\n</ul>\n<dl>\n<dd>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mi>tanh</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n        <mi>i</mi>\n        <mi>tan</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mi>i</mi>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle \\tanh x=-i\\tan(ix)}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/a937a86f39b1074cb48e6b456feeb9caa4aa1644" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:19.923ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="\\tanh x=-i\\tan(ix)" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<ul>\n<li>Hyperbolic cotangent:</li>\n</ul>\n<dl>\n<dd>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mi>coth</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mi>i</mi>\n        <mi>cot</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mi>i</mi>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle \\coth x=i\\cot(ix)}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/29250aab3051cce694b7be6b656a27c9c480daff" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:17.584ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="\\coth x=i\\cot(ix)" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<ul>\n<li>Hyperbolic secant:</li>\n</ul>\n<dl>\n<dd>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mi>sech</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mi>sec</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mi>i</mi>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle \\operatorname {sech} x=\\sec(ix)}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/96e5b1fddd2d57f35dbff1063164709021506f38" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:16.147ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="\\operatorname {sech} x=\\sec(ix)" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<ul>\n<li>Hyperbolic cosecant:</li>\n</ul>\n<dl>\n<dd>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mi>csch</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mi>i</mi>\n        <mi>csc</mi>\n        <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mi>i</mi>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle \\operatorname {csch} x=i\\csc(ix)}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/2d7d4960cf3012d6f7e7d3a3e509e29d53aef1c7" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:17.347ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="\\operatorname {csch} x=i\\csc(ix)" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p>where <i>i</i> is the <a href="/wiki/Imaginary_unit" title="Imaginary unit">imaginary unit</a> with the property that <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <msup>\n          <mi>i</mi>\n          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </msup>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n        <mn>1.</mn>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle i^{2}=-1.}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/52ca91534578075175b2088069fb6a9a414eaa7b" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:8.632ex; height:2.676ex;" alt="{\\displaystyle i^{2}=-1.}" /></span></p>\n<p>The <a href="/wiki/Complex_number" title="Complex number">complex</a> forms in the definitions above derive from <a href="/wiki/Euler%27s_formula" title="Euler\'s formula">Euler\'s formula</a>.</p>\n<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Characterizing_properties">Characterizing properties</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Hyperbolic_function&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Characterizing properties">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Hyperbolic_cosine">Hyperbolic cosine</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Hyperbolic_function&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Hyperbolic cosine">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>It can be shown that the area under the curve of cosh&#160;(<i>x</i>) over a finite interval is always equal to the arc length corresponding to that interval:<sup id="cite_ref-12" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-12">[12]</a></sup></p>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mtext>area</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <msubsup>\n          <mo>&#x222B;<!-- \xe2\x88\xab --></mo>\n          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n            <mi>a</mi>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n            <mi>b</mi>\n          </mrow>\n        </msubsup>\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mi>cosh</mi>\n          <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n            <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mtext>&#xA0;</mtext>\n        <mi>d</mi>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <msubsup>\n          <mo>&#x222B;<!-- \xe2\x88\xab --></mo>\n          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n            <mi>a</mi>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n            <mi>b</mi>\n          </mrow>\n        </msubsup>\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <msqrt>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mo>+</mo>\n            <msup>\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                  <mfrac>\n                    <mi>d</mi>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mi>d</mi>\n                      <mi>x</mi>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mfrac>\n                </mrow>\n                <mi>cosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                  <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                  <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n                </mrow>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n              <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </mrow>\n            </msup>\n          </msqrt>\n        </mrow>\n        <mtext>&#xA0;</mtext>\n        <mi>d</mi>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mtext>arc length</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle {\\text{area}}=\\int _{a}^{b}{\\cosh {(x)}}\\ dx=\\int _{a}^{b}{\\sqrt {1+\\left({\\frac {d}{dx}}\\cosh {(x)}\\right)^{2}}}\\ dx={\\text{arc length}}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/d7be5c707bc8412159e78181bf29314625c72214" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -3.005ex; width:68.315ex; height:7.676ex;" alt="{\\text{area}}=\\int _{a}^{b}{\\cosh {(x)}}\\ dx=\\int _{a}^{b}{\\sqrt {1+\\left({\\frac {d}{dx}}\\cosh {(x)}\\right)^{2}}}\\ dx={\\text{arc length}}" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Hyperbolic_tangent">Hyperbolic tangent</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Hyperbolic_function&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Hyperbolic tangent">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The hyperbolic tangent is the solution to the <a href="/wiki/Differential_equation" title="Differential equation">differential equation</a> <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <msup>\n          <mi>f</mi>\n          <mo>&#x2032;</mo>\n        </msup>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mn>1</mn>\n        <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>f</mi>\n          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </msup>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle f\'=1-f^{2}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/87fc02ed1aa49cdda47ba53f1d63fef336769142" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:11.548ex; height:3.009ex;" alt="f&#039;=1-f^{2}" /></span> with f(0)=0 and the <a href="/wiki/Nonlinear" class="mw-redirect" title="Nonlinear">nonlinear</a> <a href="/wiki/Boundary_value_problem" title="Boundary value problem">boundary value problem</a>:<sup id="cite_ref-13" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-13">[13]</a></sup> <sup id="cite_ref-14" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-14">[14]</a></sup></p>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>f</mi>\n          <mo>&#x2033;</mo>\n        </msup>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>f</mi>\n          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </msup>\n        <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n        <mi>f</mi>\n        <mo>;</mo>\n        <mspace width="1em" />\n        <mi>f</mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>f</mi>\n          <mo>&#x2032;</mo>\n        </msup>\n        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n        <mi mathvariant="normal">&#x221E;<!-- \xe2\x88\x9e --></mi>\n        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle {\\frac {1}{2}}f\'\'=f^{3}-f;\\quad f(0)=f\'(\\infty )=0}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/450f0ff5ddcbf6e91dde72a58b7689fcb59aae4e" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.838ex; width:35.371ex; height:5.176ex;" alt="{\\frac {1}{2}}f&#039;&#039;=f^{3}-f;\\quad f(0)=f&#039;(\\infty )=0" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Useful_relations">Useful relations</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Hyperbolic_function&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Useful relations">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Odd and even functions:</p>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mtable columnalign="right left right left right left right left right left right left" rowspacing="3pt" columnspacing="0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em" displaystyle="true">\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>sinh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>sinh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>cosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mi>cosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n          </mtable>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}\\sinh(-x)&amp;=-\\sinh x\\\\\\cosh(-x)&amp;=\\cosh x\\end{aligned}}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/5b696f87ba704500434756826acbf192a8b54dc6" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.505ex; width:21.418ex; height:6.176ex;" alt="{\\begin{aligned}\\sinh(-x)&amp;=-\\sinh x\\\\\\cosh(-x)&amp;=\\cosh x\\end{aligned}}" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n<p>Hence:</p>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mtable columnalign="right left right left right left right left right left right left" rowspacing="3pt" columnspacing="0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em" displaystyle="true">\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>tanh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>tanh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>coth</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>coth</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>sech</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mi>sech</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>csch</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>csch</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n          </mtable>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}\\tanh(-x)&amp;=-\\tanh x\\\\\\coth(-x)&amp;=-\\coth x\\\\\\operatorname {sech} (-x)&amp;=\\operatorname {sech} x\\\\\\operatorname {csch} (-x)&amp;=-\\operatorname {csch} x\\end{aligned}}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/a8233226276f07413a0a16e990eacce699daf054" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -5.671ex; width:22.17ex; height:12.509ex;" alt="{\\begin{aligned}\\tanh(-x)&amp;=-\\tanh x\\\\\\coth(-x)&amp;=-\\coth x\\\\\\operatorname {sech} (-x)&amp;=\\operatorname {sech} x\\\\\\operatorname {csch} (-x)&amp;=-\\operatorname {csch} x\\end{aligned}}" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n<p>It can be seen that cosh <i>x</i> and sech <i>x</i> are <a href="/wiki/Even_function" class="mw-redirect" title="Even function">even functions</a>; the others are <a href="/wiki/Odd_functions" class="mw-redirect" title="Odd functions">odd functions</a>.</p>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mtable columnalign="right left right left right left right left right left right left" rowspacing="3pt" columnspacing="0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em" displaystyle="true">\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>arsech</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mi>arcosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                  <mfrac>\n                    <mn>1</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mfrac>\n                </mrow>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>arcsch</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mi>arsinh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                  <mfrac>\n                    <mn>1</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mfrac>\n                </mrow>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>arcoth</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mi>artanh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                  <mfrac>\n                    <mn>1</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mfrac>\n                </mrow>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n          </mtable>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}\\operatorname {arsech} x&amp;=\\operatorname {arcosh} {\\frac {1}{x}}\\\\\\operatorname {arcsch} x&amp;=\\operatorname {arsinh} {\\frac {1}{x}}\\\\\\operatorname {arcoth} x&amp;=\\operatorname {artanh} {\\frac {1}{x}}\\end{aligned}}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/7d5447980299ab38ac1ba4e323de31ed54017b06" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -7.291ex; margin-bottom: -0.214ex; width:21.469ex; height:16.176ex;" alt="{\\begin{aligned}\\operatorname {arsech} x&amp;=\\operatorname {arcosh} {\\frac {1}{x}}\\\\\\operatorname {arcsch} x&amp;=\\operatorname {arsinh} {\\frac {1}{x}}\\\\\\operatorname {arcoth} x&amp;=\\operatorname {artanh} {\\frac {1}{x}}\\end{aligned}}" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n<p>Hyperbolic sine and cosine satisfy:</p>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mtable columnalign="right left right left right left right left right left right left" rowspacing="3pt" columnspacing="0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em" displaystyle="true">\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>cosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo>+</mo>\n                <mi>sinh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>e</mi>\n                  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                </msup>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>cosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mi>sinh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>e</mi>\n                  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                    <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                </msup>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>cosh</mi>\n                  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </mrow>\n                </msup>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>sinh</mi>\n                  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </mrow>\n                </msup>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n          </mtable>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}\\cosh x+\\sinh x&amp;=e^{x}\\\\\\cosh x-\\sinh x&amp;=e^{-x}\\\\\\cosh ^{2}x-\\sinh ^{2}x&amp;=1\\end{aligned}}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/8c9c5a72fcd377fdd94f23141685c74790d8a30b" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -4.005ex; width:24.484ex; height:9.176ex;" alt="{\\begin{aligned}\\cosh x+\\sinh x&amp;=e^{x}\\\\\\cosh x-\\sinh x&amp;=e^{-x}\\\\\\cosh ^{2}x-\\sinh ^{2}x&amp;=1\\end{aligned}}" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n<p>the last which is similar to the <a href="/wiki/Pythagorean_trigonometric_identity" title="Pythagorean trigonometric identity">Pythagorean trigonometric identity</a>.</p>\n<p>One also has</p>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mtable columnalign="right left right left right left right left right left right left" rowspacing="3pt" columnspacing="0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em" displaystyle="true">\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>sech</mi>\n                  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </mrow>\n                </msup>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>tanh</mi>\n                  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </mrow>\n                </msup>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>csch</mi>\n                  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </mrow>\n                </msup>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>coth</mi>\n                  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </mrow>\n                </msup>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2212;<!-- \xe2\x88\x92 --></mo>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n          </mtable>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}\\operatorname {sech} ^{2}x&amp;=1-\\tanh ^{2}x\\\\\\operatorname {csch} ^{2}x&amp;=\\coth ^{2}x-1\\end{aligned}}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/dd7702db14d3d79fdff3ba95a87fdbd044a5ea36" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.671ex; width:22.471ex; height:6.509ex;" alt="{\\begin{aligned}\\operatorname {sech} ^{2}x&amp;=1-\\tanh ^{2}x\\\\\\operatorname {csch} ^{2}x&amp;=\\coth ^{2}x-1\\end{aligned}}" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n<p>for the other functions.</p>\n<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Sums_of_arguments">Sums of arguments</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Hyperbolic_function&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Sums of arguments">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>\n<dl>\n<dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" >\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">\n        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">\n          <mtable columnalign="right left right left right left right left right left right left" rowspacing="3pt" columnspacing="0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em" displaystyle="true">\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>sinh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo>+</mo>\n                <mi>y</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mi>sinh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n                <mi>cosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>y</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n                <mo>+</mo>\n                <mi>cosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n                <mi>sinh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>y</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n            </mtr>\n            <mtr>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi>cosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo>+</mo>\n                <mi>y</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n              </mtd>\n              <mtd>\n                <mi></mi>\n                <mo>=</mo>\n                <mi>cosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n                <mi>cosh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n                <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>\n                <mi>y</mi>\n                <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>\n                <mo>+</mo>\n                <mi>sinh</mi>\n                <mo>&#x2061;<!-- \xe2\x81\xa1 --></mo>\n        